          <msContents>
            <summary>[p]Alemanus of Bohemia and others, alchemical and herbal miscellany[/p]
[p]Written in a semi-current humanist hand, 16-17 lines to a page: a few initials in red.[/p]
[p][b]Contents[/b][/p]

[p]1. ff. 1r-16r Alemanus of Bohemia, [i]On the stone to Boniface VIII[/i][/p]
[p]f. 1r Bonifacio octavo sumo papa de la sancta Clezia Romana Maistro Alemano de Boemia se recomanda ... f. 16r ... con lingua. Deo gracias. Amen.[/p]
[p]2. ff. 16r-22v Alchemical and medical recipes in Latin[/p]
[p]3. ff. 23r-26v Treatise on the seven herbs and seven planets[/p]
[p]f. 23r La prima erba sien del sole ... f. 26v ... i demunis. De gracias.[/p]
[p]4. ff. 27r-28v Treatise on herbs, end wanting[/p][p]f. 27r De vitutibus elintropie. Prima erba apud caldeos vocatur yreos ... f. 28v ... commisce cum ... [/p]</summary>
